  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/17202`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `नौचालन के लिए सामुद्रिक सहायता अधिनियम, 2021`
  actYear (2021)
  ministry `Ministry of Ports, Shipping and Waterways`
  department undefined
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the development, maintenance and management of aids to navigation in India; for training and certification of operator of aids to navigation, development of its historical, educational and cultural value; to ensure compliance with the obligation under the maritime treaties and international instruments to which India is a party and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
